OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778186663
OL,3,CInfantino promises to bring $2m World
OL,4,CCup ticket buyers 'a hot dog and a
OL,5,CCoke'
OL,7,FFifa president Gianni Infantino has
OL,8,Fpromised to "personally bring a hot
OL,9,Fdog and a Coke" to anyone willing to
OL,10,Fpurchase a $2 million ticket to the
OL,11,FMen's World Cup Final.
OL,13,FSpeaking at the Milken Institute
OL,14,FGlobal Conference in Beverly Hills on
OL,15,FThursday, Infantino defended the high
OL,16,Fticket prices for this summer's World
OL,17,FCup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
