OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778186663
OL,3,CInfantino promises to bring $2m World
OL,4,CCup ticket buyers 'a hot dog and a
OL,5,CCoke'
OL,7,FFifa has faced criticism over the
OL,8,Fticket pricing and particularly over
OL,9,Fthe decision to adopt dynamic pricing,
OL,10,Fwhere costs rise or fall depending on
OL,11,Fdemand.
OL,13,FThose who choose to resell their
OL,14,Fticket can also list them at a much
OL,15,Fhigher price than they originally
OL,16,Fpaid, even on FIFA's official resale
OL,17,Fsite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778186663
OL,3,CInfantino promises to bring $2m World
OL,4,CCup ticket buyers 'a hot dog and a
OL,5,CCoke'
OL,7,FInfantino said: "If some people put on
OL,8,Fthe resale market some tickets for the
OL,9,Ffinal at $2 million (#1.47 million),
OL,10,Fnumber one, it doesn't mean that the
OL,11,Ftickets cost $2 million, and number
OL,12,Ftwo, it doesn't mean that somebody
OL,13,Fwill buy these tickets."
OL,15,F"And if somebody buys a ticket for the
OL,16,Ffinal for $2 million, I will
OL,17,Fpersonally bring a hot dog and a Coke
OL,18,Fto make sure that he has a great
OL,19,Fexperience!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
