PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778186663
OL,3,CInfantino promises to bring $2m World
OL,4,CCup ticket buyers 'a hot dog and a
OL,5,CCoke'
OL,7,FFootball Supporters Europe (FSE) and
OL,8,FEuroconsumers have lodged complaints
OL,9,Fwith the European Commission after
OL,10,Ffans who are part of national team
OL,11,Ftravel clubs and loyalty schemes were
OL,12,Fgiven an initial cheapest ticket for
OL,13,Fthe final of more than #3,000.
OL,15,FLast week, Fifa's World Cup ticket
OL,16,Fresale website listed four tickets to
OL,17,Fthe same game for $2.3 million (#1.47
OL,18,Fmillion) each.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
