OL,3,CInfantino promises to bring $2m World
OL,4,CCup ticket buyers 'a hot dog and a
OL,5,CCoke'
OL,7,FFifa does not control the asking price
OL,8,Fon its site but does take a 15%
OL,9,Fpurchase fee from each buyer and 15%
OL,10,Fresale fee from each seller.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
