CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778186663
OL,3,CInfantino promises to bring $2m World
OL,4,CCup ticket buyers 'a hot dog and a
OL,5,CCoke'
OL,7,FInfantino defended the resale market
OL,8,Fand said: "If you were to sell tickets
OL,9,Fat the price which is too low, these
OL,10,Ftickets will be resold at a much
OL,11,Fhigher price and as a matter of fact,
OL,12,Fwe have 25 per cent of the group-stage
OL,13,Ftickets which can be bought for less
OL,14,Fthan $300 dollars."
OL,16,FHe went on to compare the ticket
OL,17,Fprices with US college sports and said
OL,18,Fyou could not get a ticket "for less
OL,19,Fthan $300 dollars. And this is the
OL,20,FWorld Cup!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
